item.title: Men’s Football beat King’s in ULU plate final
item.author: Haran Rajkumar,
item.description: An incredible season of football for Imperial College Football Club culminated in two cup finals, having already seen a league win for the 4s, and a narrow miss on promotion for the 3s. With the 1s cup final played on the Saturday, the 5s were out to set the cup final bar on the preceding Wednesday. …
